{"tid":371042,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"測試測試測試測試測試測試","createTime":"2017-08-23T11:41:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T15:13:03.000Z","uid":139505,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"153b1a6ae761215652c6b6982db7b5cc29f66a4a","tid":371042,"uid":139505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:41:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>[Frankfurt, Germany] 旅程的起點</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/tYBG7LO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FtYBG7LO.jpg&h=8fe7ddfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n法蘭克褔歐洲央行總部<br />\n <br />\n這是一個起點。<br />\n <br />\n究竟是什麼驅使我第一次到歐洲?<br />\n <br />\n&quot;人一世物一世, 咩都要試下&quot;<br />\n <br />\n&quot;去歐洲好威威呀!&quot;<br />\n <br />\n&quot;如果唔趁Grad trip去, 以後冇機會放咁長假去ga la&quot;<br />\n <br />\n&quot;聽講住hostel可以識到台妹&quot;<br />\n <br />\n&quot;企o係The Amazing Race既Check Point&quot;<br />\n <br />\n四年前的事情, 已經不太記得為什麼當時有動力去規劃一個廿七天到歐洲的旅程, 只記得籌備過程經歷很多不快, 不過最終都順利出發, 不知道是好事還是壞事, 因為...<br />\n <br />\n這次旅行令我愛上長途旅行, 一年不去過一次總是不心息!<br />\n <br />\n哈哈, 年輕應該要多點闖蕩吧!在我心中, 德國法蘭克褔就是我第一次歐遊的起點, 也是我每一次長途旅行的起點。<br />\n <br />\n27日旅程, 出發前的行程:<br />\n <br />\nFrankfurt (萊茵河)<br />\nHeidelberg<br />\nWurzburg<br />\nRothenburg ob der Tauber<br />\nAugsburg<br />\nFussen<br />\nGarmisch-Partenkirchen (Zugspitze)<br />\nMunich<br />\nSalzburg (St Wolgang, Konigsee)<br />\nBudapest<br />\nVienna<br />\nČesk&yacute; Krumlov<br />\nPrague<br />\nParis"},{"pid":"757d909c8b1f1fe8d59e23386fa0020c1270af7b","tid":371042,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:42:13.000Z","msg":"frankfurt係咪好多腸食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b79351be527fec317384b7b3d41257f24a5e7b6","tid":371042,"uid":139505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:43:02.000Z","msg":"SOR, 諗住試下post唔post到, 唔小心開左post"},{"pid":"d9162d06db69